Move message to a label/folder

Usage: mxr move [OPTIONS] <LABEL> [MESSAGE_ID]

Arguments:
  <LABEL>       Target label
  [MESSAGE_ID]  Message ID

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>  
      --yes              
      --dry-run          
  -h, --help             Print help
